#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:325
msgid "\"Abandon hope\" was merely a suggestion. The gate makes it mandatory."
msgstr "\"Abandon hope\" was merely a suggestion. The gate makes it mandatory."

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:195
msgid "\"Aim? I aim at everything. The fire sorts out the rest.\""
msgstr "\"Aim? I aim at everything. The fire sorts out the rest.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:335
msgid "\"All roads lead here eventually. I've simply removed the 'eventually.'\""
msgstr "\"All roads lead here eventually. I've simply removed the 'eventually.'\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:288
msgid "\"Answer my riddle and pass. Fail, and become part of the question.\""
msgstr "\"Answer my riddle and pass. Fail, and become part of the question.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:297
msgid "\"Death is not an ending. It's a warm-up.\""
msgstr "\"Death is not an ending. It's a warm-up.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:289
msgid "\"Father made the wings. I learned what he never could — how to fall.\""
msgstr "\"Father made the wings. I learned what he never could — how to fall.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:193
msgid "\"Hold the line. Not for glory, but because the man beside you would do the same.\""
msgstr "\"Hold the line. Not for glory, but because the man beside you would do the same.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:363
msgid "\"I am the answer to every prayer you were afraid to speak.\""
msgstr "\"I am the answer to every prayer you were afraid to speak.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:361
msgid "\"I believe.\" Two words. Infinite consequences."
msgstr "\"I believe.\" Two words. Infinite consequences."

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:235
msgid "\"I didn't start the fire. I just made sure it couldn't stop.\""
msgstr "\"I didn't start the fire. I just made sure it couldn't stop.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:241
msgid "\"I didn't steal it. I liberated it from the burden of ownership.\""
msgstr "\"I didn't steal it. I liberated it from the burden of ownership.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:277
msgid "\"I died here. Now so will everything else.\""
msgstr "\"I died here. Now so will everything else.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:269
msgid "\"I do not judge the dead. I judge what they did while living.\""
msgstr "\"I do not judge the dead. I judge what they did while living.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:342
msgid "\"I don't turn men into swine. I reveal the swine they already are.\""
msgstr "\"I don't turn men into swine. I reveal the swine they already are.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:222
msgid "\"I have looked upon every truth. I recommend ignorance.\""
msgstr "\"I have looked upon every truth. I recommend ignorance.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:213
msgid "\"I see just fine. I only need to see you once.\""
msgstr "\"I see just fine. I only need to see you once.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:338
msgid "\"I was hired for the party. Nobody said anything about the apocalypse.\""
msgstr "\"I was hired for the party. Nobody said anything about the apocalypse.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:304
msgid "\"I'm not fat. I'm aerodynamically generous.\""
msgstr "\"I'm not fat. I'm aerodynamically generous.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:232
msgid "\"Kill one head, two more shall rise.\" The math alone should terrify you."
msgstr "\"Kill one head, two more shall rise.\" The math alone should terrify you."

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:318
msgid "\"Kiss it? I'm going to EAT it.\""
msgstr "\"Kiss it? I'm going to EAT it.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:329
msgid "\"Lead from the dark. Strike from the dark. Return to the dark.\""
msgstr "\"Lead from the dark. Strike from the dark. Return to the dark.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:282
msgid "\"My heel? I fixed that.\""
msgstr "\"My heel? I fixed that.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:252
msgid "\"Nothing is wasted. Everything feeds something.\""
msgstr "\"Nothing is wasted. Everything feeds something.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:296
msgid "\"Peace is the dream of the weak. War is the only honest conversation.\""
msgstr "\"Peace is the dream of the weak. War is the only honest conversation.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:311
msgid "\"Release the —\" Actually, it released itself."
msgstr "\"Release the —\" Actually, it released itself."

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:336
msgid "\"Round and round it goes. Where it stops, nobody chose.\""
msgstr "\"Round and round it goes. Where it stops, nobody chose.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:321
msgid "\"The dead follow orders better than the living. They've learned what disobedience costs.\""
msgstr "\"The dead follow orders better than the living. They've learned what disobedience costs.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:265
msgid "\"The future is certain.\" \"The future is impossible.\" Both heads are always right."
msgstr "\"The future is certain.\" \"The future is impossible.\" Both heads are always right."

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:333
msgid "\"The gryphon chose me. I'm still not sure if that's an honor or a threat.\""
msgstr "\"The gryphon chose me. I'm still not sure if that's an honor or a threat.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:331
msgid "\"The horse knows the way to battle. I just hold on.\""
msgstr "\"The horse knows the way to battle. I just hold on.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:328
msgid "\"The loudest victories make no sound at all.\""
msgstr "\"The loudest victories make no sound at all.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:292
msgid "\"The north wind is not cruel. It simply does not care.\""
msgstr "\"The north wind is not cruel. It simply does not care.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:239
msgid "\"The sands shift. I remain.\""
msgstr "\"The sands shift. I remain.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:339
msgid "\"Two enter, one leaves. Unless I'm having a good day — then none leave.\""
msgstr "\"Two enter, one leaves. Unless I'm having a good day — then none leave.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:208
msgid "\"We do not ride into battle. We ARE the charge.\""
msgstr "\"We do not ride into battle. We ARE the charge.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:284
msgid "\"We don't fight like men. We fight like something men should fear.\""
msgstr "\"We don't fight like men. We fight like something men should fear.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:272
msgid "\"We were ants once. We remember what it means to carry a hundred times our weight.\""
msgstr "\"We were ants once. We remember what it means to carry a hundred times our weight.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:340
msgid "\"Wine is truth. And truth, my friend, is absolutely hammered right now.\""
msgstr "\"Wine is truth. And truth, my friend, is absolutely hammered right now.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:225
msgid "\"Wisdom is knowing which battles to fight. I am here to remind you this is not one of them.\""
msgstr "\"Wisdom is knowing which battles to fight. I am here to remind you this is not one of them.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:285
msgid "\"You came here for answers. You won't like them, but you came anyway.\""
msgstr "\"You came here for answers. You won't like them, but you came anyway.\""

#: src/lib/card-identity.ts:199
msgid "\"You cannot catch what was never where you looked.\""
msgstr "\"You cannot catch what was never where you looked.\""

